data.title: Kenneth Branagh Appears on "Rosie," June 6
data.meta_description: Actor and director Kenneth Branagh will be a guest on "The Rosie O'Donnell Show" on June 6. Branagh will be promoting his new film adaptation of Shakespeare's "Love's Labour's Lost."
data.text:
News Kenneth Branagh Appears on "Rosie," June 6 Actor and director Kenneth Branagh will be a guest on "The Rosie O'Donnell Show" on June 6. Branagh will be promoting his new film adaptation of Shakespeare's "Love's Labour's Lost."

Actor and director Kenneth Branagh will be a guest on "The Rosie O'Donnell Show" on June 6. Branagh will be promoting his new film adaptation of Shakespeare's "Love's Labour's Lost." O'Donnell's show airs in New York on channel 7 at 10 AM. Check local listing for times and stations.

--By Robert Simonson
